" Use ; for : to avoid using the Shift key
nnoremap ; :
vnoremap ; :

" Press Enter to save in normal mode
nnoremap <CR> :w<CR>

" A more accessible escape key.
inoremap jk <Esc>
inoremap JK <Esc>
inoremap Jk <Esc>
inoremap jK <Esc>

" remap U to <C-r> for easier redo
" from http://vimbits.com/bits/356
nnoremap U <C-r>
